Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.10,0:53:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalamure were domesticated long before Din.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.82,0:53:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, the practice was lost for many years\Nbefore it was rediscovered by Highmarch merchants.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.77,0:53:44.83,Top,,0,0,0,,[garbled chrrrp sound]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.31,0:53:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.31,0:53:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They are medium-sized mounts, ranging from\N 15 hands to 20 hands, depending;
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.66,0:53:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,originally bred for more vocational purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.47,0:54:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ostudans were bred for long-hauling cargo and wares.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.48,0:54:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Marsh Hoppers were used across the wetlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.02,0:54:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the mountains, we find the Boulder Ridge climbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.79,0:54:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[chirrp noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.97,0:54:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Their powerful legs and claws granting them their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.45,0:54:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, smaller, leaner breeds became\Nrecreational racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.32,0:54:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Entertainment for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.16,0:54:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Every ward and their nobility is matched with a dalamure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.18,0:54:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are bred specifically for the people of the crown,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.53,0:54:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and while the colours and patterns on the\Ncoats and feathers change frequently and drastically,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.56,0:54:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the more refined breeders have perfected\Nthe colours of the Wards.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.34,0:54:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They imprint on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.50,0:54:45.76,Top,,0,0,0,,[chrrr noise]
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.01,0:54:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it is not uncommon to see blinders\Nattached to the dalamure harness,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.65,0:54:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,requiring the creature to rely on sound,\Ncommand, or magic to guide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.70,0:54:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The armour is intricate and fanciful,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.86,0:55:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with their human companions donning armour\Nand masks to match;
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.01,0:55:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,adorned with feathers, jewels, and sometimes\Neven dynlet stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.13,0:55:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalamures imprint for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.49,0:55:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not to say they cannot be useful, or\Nused, by anyone other than the one chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.04,0:55:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.91,0:55:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they will never bond, or be as devoted, as\Nthey are to their companion of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.86,0:55:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Once bound, a dalamure lives its entire life mute,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.88,0:55:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging on every word its companion utters.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.50,0:55:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Should their half fall before they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.13,0:55:38.30,Top,,0,0,0,,[chrrrping]
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.30,0:55:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the dalamure begins to vocalise,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.91,0:55:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,repeating sayings and phrases of their lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.42,0:55:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[garbled, corrupted] Slow up, now. Slow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.54,0:55:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[chrrping]
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.18,0:55:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,either out of grief, some say, or perhaps a strong recollection.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.27,0:55:49.06,Top,,0,0,0,,[garbled] Easy, now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.91,0:55:49.94,Top,,0,0,0,,[chrrrrp]
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.81,0:55:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This resonance is seen as abhorrent to many in Din
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.58,0:55:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and these faithful mounts are usually put down,\N so that both companions can be truly laid to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.03,0:56:04.67,Top,,0,0,0,,[distorted] Who's a pretty boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.02,0:56:06.80,Top,,0,0,0,,[chrrrp]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.12,0:56:10.62,Top,,0,0,0,,[chrrrp]
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.92,0:56:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[distorted] I'll miss you.
